          "durationMs": 7000
        },
        {
          "trigger": "step_1",
          "text": "Karoo succulents can survive 18 months without rain.\nEvolution discovered immortality through patience.",
          "durationMs": 7000
        },
        {
          "trigger": "step_2",
          "text": "At night, the Karoo has some of the darkest skies on Earth.\nThe Square Kilometre Array — humanity's largest telescope — was built here.\nWe come to the oldest places to look the farthest.",
