        {
          "trigger": "step_1",
          "text": "Arashiyama bamboo grove in Kyoto is so loud in wind\nit was designated one of Japan's 100 Soundscapes to Preserve.\nSound as cultural heritage.",
          "durationMs": 8000
        },
        {
          "trigger": "step_2",
          "text": "Bamboo sequesters carbon 35% faster than an equivalent hardwood forest.\nAnd it regrows without replanting.\nThe climate solution was always here — we just called it a garden.",
